<h2 id="splunk-lisence">splunk lisence</h2>
<p>for buying splunk lisence we create RFP and estimate EPS and sizing of storage.</p>
<ul>
  <li>RFP = request for proposal</li>
  <li>ESP = Event per secend</li>
</ul>

<h2 id="splunk-storage-sizing"><a href="https://splunk-sizing.appspot.com/">Splunk Storage Sizing</a></h2>
<p>Specify the amount of time to retain data for each category. Data will be rolled through each category dependant on its age.</p>

<ul>
  <li>Hot storage  = NVME,SSD -&gt; 30day</li>
  <li>Warm storage = HDD,SAS 15k  -&gt; 6 mon</li>
  <li>Cold storage = 10k,tape  -&gt; 1 year</li>
</ul>

